name: Nvidia
recommandation: NVIDIA's core GPU and AI products could be classified as high-risk under Articles 6 and 8-15, requiring conformity assessments, risk management, data governance, and human oversight controls. Certain AI practices like manipulative techniques (Article 5) may also be restricted. NVIDIA has significant revenue exposure to AI and data center applications that could be impacted by the regulation. Its supply chain and key markets like China also face regulatory risks. Closely monitor regulatory developments and engage with policymakers. Invest in compliance capabilities for high-risk AI products. Diversify into less AI-intensive applications like gaming and professional visualization.
